- Kuba intangarugero ku bana b’abahungu n’ab’abakobwa kandi ku buryo
  bungana;
- Gushishikariza umwana kugaragaza ibimurimo, ibyo yemera no gukemura
  ibibazo;
- Kumenya no gushyigikira umwana mu byo ashoboye n’ibyo atemo
  imbogamizi;
- Guha umwana umwanya uhagije, ukamuganiriza kandi ukam-wumva;
- Gushaka ibikorwa mwakorera hamwe kugira ngo umwana yumve ko ashoboye,
  ate umutekano kandi akunzwe;
- Gufasha no gushyigikira umwana igihe akina na bagenzi be no mu bindi
  bikorwa bitari muri gahunda y’amasomo;
- Gushishikariza umwana imyitwarire myiza ukanamubwira ibyo agomba
  kwirinda;
- Gukurikirana umwana ku ishuri uzirikana ko Se w’umwana,
- Nyina n’undi wese umwitaho ari bo barimu be ba mbere.
